title: Large 1 Bedroom w/ Washer, Dryer, and Brand New Flooring!
posting_body: ['Enjoy our Sparkling Pool!', 'Welcome Home to Rainier Pointe', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 40', 'OR Text', '40', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'Rainier Pointe', '6643 20th St E, Fife, WA, 98424', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 658 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Just minutes from Tacoma, Rainier Pointe Apartments are close to everything!', 'These garden-style homes offer an escape from the hustle of the city with fantastic views of Mount Rainier and plenty of access to recreation.', 'Features', '- Washer & Dryer', '- Wood Burning Fireplace', '- 24-Hour Fitness Center w Inside Basketball Court', '- Renovated Units*', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '*in select units', 'Community Amenities', '- Cabana', '- Outdoor Heated Pool', '- Garages', '- Fitness Center', '- Clubhouse', '- Playground', '- Dog Park', '- Covered Parking*', 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome up to two pets per home both cats and dogs.', 'There is a $500 fee and $250 of it is refundable for each pet.', 'Please call our leasing office for more details.', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5 times the rent amount', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'kYhONhZ0pvso']
